**** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
**** {{topt|River Lum.}}
**** {{topt|Sack.}}
**** {{topt|Spider web.}}
**** {{topt|Basket.}}
***** '''Cook:''' Congratulations, that's the right answer.
***** '''Cook:''' Here is the Hosidius milk I promised.
***** {{tbox|pic=Hosidius milk detail.png|You receive a bottle of Hosidius milk.}}
***** {{tact|end}}
**** {{topt|Bucket.}}
