==Special spices==
===Talking to Eggy===
* '''Eggy:''' The boss has instructed me to tell you to go talk to Martin.
* '''Eggy:''' Also, don't forget to mention Special spices and bring me some carrots would ya please!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Martin===
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Ask about the Skillcape of Farming.|event=no}}
* {{topt|Ask about the quest.|event=no}}
* {{topt|Talk about Easter.}}
** '''Player:''' Hello Martin, I hear from the Easter Bunny that you are the man to talk about spices.
** '''Martin the Master Gardener:''' You what?
** '''Player:''' Some may say you are, the spice man.
** '''Martin the Master Gardener:''' I'm terribly sorry but I don't understand what you mean.
** '''Player:''' What did that bunny say again?
** {{tselect|What did the Easter Bunny tell you to say to martin?{{Sic}}}}
** {{topt|Spicy spices.}}
*** '''Player:''' Spicy spices?
*** '''Martin the Master Gardener:''' Sorry mate, I haven't the foggiest idea what you're on about. Now please leave me alone.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Special spices.}}
*** '''Player:''' Special spices?
*** '''Martin the Master Gardener:''' Oh! I understand now. The Easter Bunny is making some fuel and he needs the Special Spice blend for the mixture.
*** '''Player:''' Sorry I didn't say sooner. I had to think for a moment what the Easter Bunny asked me to do.
*** '''Martin the Master Gardener:''' That's ok, I understand.
*** '''Player:''' So can I get some Special spices please?
*** '''Martin the Master Gardener:''' Sure you can, but first I need you to take this Fine silk to Aggie. I need it dyed red before I can use it. You can do that for me, can't you?
*** '''Player:''' Sure I can, just hand the Fine silk over and I will get right on it.
*** {{tbox|pic=Fine silk detail.png|You receive some Fine silk.}}
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Sweaty spices.}}
*** '''Player:''' Sweaty spices?
*** '''Martin the Master Gardener:''' Sorry mate, I haven't the foggiest idea what you're on about. Now please leave me alone.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Sweet spices.}}
*** '''Player:''' Sweet spices?
*** '''Martin the Master Gardener:''' Sorry mate, I haven't the foggiest idea what you're on about. Now please leave me alone.
*** {{tact|end}}

===Bringing the silk to Aggie===
* '''Aggie:''' What can I help you with?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|What could you make for me?|event=no}}
* {{topt|Cool, do you turn people into frogs?|event=no}}
* {{topt|You mad old witch, you can't help me.|event=no}}
* {{topt|Can you make dyes for me please?|event=no}}
* {{topt|Ask about dyeing Martin's silk.}}
** '''Player:''' Hello there Aggie, Martin wants to ask if you are able to dye this Fine silk red for him.
** '''Aggie:''' Sure I can, but you will need to give me a Tomato as well. You can have the one on the floor by the mirror.
** '''Aggie:''' Do you have all the items I require?
** {{tcond|If the player doesn't have a tomato:}}
*** '''Player:''' Not just yet, let me go get them.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player has a tomato:}}
