*** {{tact|end}}

===Bringing the red silk to Martin===
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Ask about the Skillcape of Farming.|event=no}}
* {{topt|Ask about the quest.|event=no}}
* {{topt|Talk about Easter.}}
** '''Martin the Master Gardener:''' Have you dyed the Fine silk for me yet?
** '''Player:''' Why yes I have, here you go.
** '''Martin the Master Gardener:''' Marvellous, here are the Special spices I promised you.
** {{tbox|pic=Fine red silk detail.png|pic2=Special spices detail.png|You give the Fine red silk to Martin in exchange for the Special spices.}}
** '''Player:''' Thanks a bunch Martin, you've been a good egg.
** '''Martin the Master Gardener:''' Don't make me laugh!
** {{tact|end}}

