===Special spices===
* {{tbox|pic=Special spices detail.png|You hand over the Special spices to the Easter Bunny.}}
* '''Easter Bunny:''' That seems to be everything.
* '''Easter Bunny:''' Thanks a bunch mate, you did a cracking job getting all the ingredients for me.
