==Mixing the mixture with Party Pete==
* '''Player:''' Hi!
* '''Party Pete:''' Hi! I'm Party Pete. Welcome to the Party Room!
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|So what's this room for?|event=no}}
* {{topt|What's the big lever over there for?|event=no}}
* {{topt|What's the gold chest for?|event=no}}
* {{topt|The Easter Bunny needs your help.}}
** '''Player:''' Party Pete, the Easter Bunny needs your help!
** '''Party Pete:''' What's wrong?
** '''Player:''' It's terrible, the Easter Bunny's egg making machine and mixing machine have both ran out of fuel.
** '''Party Pete:''' So why doesn't the Easter Bunny add more fuel?
** '''Player:''' That's the problem, there is no more fuel left.
** '''Player:''' But the Easter Bunny sent me on a few errands to get ingredients for more fuel. Now we have a mixture that is unmixed because the mixing machine is out of fuel.
** '''Player:''' So the Easter Bunny thought that since you are a cracking dancer, you could mix the fuel by dancing.
** '''Player:''' Can you try and mix the mixture for the Easter Bunny please?
** '''Party Pete:''' I would consider myself the chosen egg if I am able to help the Easter Bunny out.
** {{tbox|pic=Chocolate mixture(u) detail.png|You give the mixture to Party Pete}}
** '''Player:''' Give it a go Party Pete.
** '''Party Pete:''' Let's give this a try.
** {{qact|Party Pete performs the giant easter egg dance emote.}}
** '''Party Pete:''' I did it! The mixture is now mixed together!
** '''Party Pete:''' Here you go, you better take this back to the Easter Bunny on the double.
** {{tbox|pic=Choco serum detail.png|You receive a bottle of Choco serum}}
** '''Player:''' Those were some eggcelent moves there Party Pete! Thanks a bunch!
** '''Party Pete:''' All in a day's work.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|More options.|event=no}}

===Back to the Easter Bunny===
* '''Easter Bunny:''' Have you spoken to Party Pete in the Falador Party Room yet?
* '''Player:''' Yes, and his dancing was amazing! I didn't know Party Pete could crack a move like that!
* '''Easter Bunny:''' Well that's why he's called Party Pete. Now can I have the fuel please?
* '''Player:''' Yes of course, here is the fuel for your machines!
* {{tbox|pic=Choco serum detail.png|You hand the Choco serum over to the Easter Bunny.}}
* '''Easter Bunny:''' Eggcelent! Now my machines will be hopping around for the rest of Easter!
* '''Easter Bunny:''' Thanks for helping me adventurer! You're such a good egg.
* '''Player:''' Happy to help Mr Bunny.
* '''Easter Bunny:''' Please take this, it's a very special egg just for you!
* {{tbox|pic=Giant easter egg detail.png|The Easter Bunny pulls a giant Easter egg from his burrow and hands it to you.}}
